          "Prague countryside",
          "",
          "Generation",
          "Neonate 11"
        ],
        [],
        [
          "Who You Know",
          "Your relationship to these people is described. This may mean they do not know you."
        ],
        [
          "Don Paul Guzman",
          "Archbishop of Los Angeles, - He is a strong supporter of mortal faiths in the sabbat. He also has travled the holy lands and would be a good conection to find what you seek."
        ],
        [],
        [],
        [],
        [
          "Starting Goals",
          "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        ],
        [
          "Find make sure the profit of your pack is safe, he is a connection to the trueness of the trinity, and a connection to the proof of gods work."
        ],
        [
          "Convince others of the supremacy of the path Cain"
        ],
        [
          "Use the resources of your pack to find other evidences of True Faith and God like miracles in the city of Los Angeles. Failing that, find the demons they are as much a proof as angles for the non belivers."
        ],
